sentences: Ilson Amâncio Carreiro Júnior (born June 26, 1991 in Belo Horizonte), better known as Junior Carreiro, is a Brazilian retired footballer.
He is now a football agent registered with the Brazilian Football Confederation.
He started his professional career at Náutico in 2009.
He signed with D.C. United in 2010 and moved to Salgueiro in 2012.

Carreiro is the younger brother of Fred Carreiro, his teammate at D.C. United in 2011.
